y pieces. Only with these key pieces can players progress to the second stage, which contains the exit points that allow innocent players to end the game.<br><br><br><strong>STRANGE TOWN</strong> is a fantastic game to play with your friends. <strong>Add it to your wish list and let your friends know!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1688400106\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740250/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1688400106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
